1
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:41,030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 13]

3
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,310
Mr. Ji,

4
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,759
please wait a moment.

5
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:04,540
This is the money
I borrowed from you last time.

6
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:05,960
There's no need to rush to pay me back.

7
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,130
Please take it.

8
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:09,220
Otherwise, I'll feel bad.

9
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:12,780
Okay.

10
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:16,920
Is there anything else?

11
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:22,690
Have the linens in the room been changed?

12
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,420
Yes, they have.

13
00:02:23,420 --> 00:02:24,550
What did the guest say?

14
00:02:24,550 --> 00:02:26,210
No negative feedback for now.

15
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:28,960
Okay.

16
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,760
Go back to your work.

17
00:02:38,550 --> 00:02:40,410
You're getting off work soon too.

18
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:49,010
Yunhai Cotton Textile Factory

19
00:02:49,010 --> 00:02:50,240
is a solid partner.

20
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:52,010
This time, the PR crisis

21
00:02:52,010 --> 00:02:53,820
was handled smoothly in the end.

22
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,190
Thanks to you.

23
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,560
Thank you.

24
00:02:59,079 --> 00:02:59,740
No problem.

25
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,030
What about the linens

26
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,800
you ordered from abroad?

27
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:05,960
They are also in storage.

28
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,710
Shanghai is humid,

29
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:08,970
so it's always right to have an extra set.

30
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,430
How come you know so much about linens?

31
00:03:13,950 --> 00:03:15,550
Shouldn't I know about them?

32
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:17,640
That's not what I meant.

33
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,430
I used to work at Purong Hotel

34
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,960
as an attendant for many years.

35
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,500
I've experienced

36
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:27,960
all the work you've done

37
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,240
and the mistakes you've made.

38
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,310
No wonder.

39
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,430
No wonder what?

40
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,460
No wonder

41
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:34,960
you can always find
so many faults with me.

42
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:35,960
I can't help it.

43
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,640
It's your first time being a forewoman.

44
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,850
And it's my first time officially
being a general manager.

45
00:03:39,850 --> 00:03:41,079
Let's help each other

46
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,760
and bear with each other.

47
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:50,240
Actually, what I want to do
is very simple.

48
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:52,290
I just want to be a good forewoman.

49
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,700
But...

50
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:55,910
But what?

51
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:58,079
But we got through

52
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,400
this crisis together

53
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,930
as a whole executive floor.

54
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,080
But I was the only one who got the bonus.

55
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,840
Everyone thinks I got it
through connections.

56
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:09,280
What do you think then?

57
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:11,750
If you think I gave you that bonus

58
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:12,910
because I've lost my mind

59
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,150
or was playing favorites,

60
00:04:14,150 --> 00:04:15,400
and you really don't want it,

61
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,060
you can return it to the hotel.

62
00:04:17,290 --> 00:04:18,310
If you had the guts to play favorites,

63
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:20,310
I wouldn't dare to receive it, okay?

64
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,950
You really are quite different.

65
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:26,800
Others bully the weak and fear the strong,

66
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,600
but you do the exact opposite.

67
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,390
If you used this momentum

68
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:32,830
to manage your subordinates,
it would be great.

69
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:33,490
Look at you.

70
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:35,990
You act like being a forewoman
is accumulating karma.

71
00:04:35,990 --> 00:04:36,830
You are everywhere—

72
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:37,680
working overtime,

73
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,159
covering shifts,

74
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:38,920
taking extra duty…

75
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,390
You don't seriously think
the executive floor

76
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,870
can keep everything running smoothly

77
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,430
just by this kind of
unconditional self-sacrifice, do you?

78
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,600
I know.

79
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,510
Sometimes I want to be tough too.

80
00:04:47,590 --> 00:04:50,780
But if they don't respect me
from the bottom of their hearts,

81
00:04:50,780 --> 00:04:53,159
my toughness is just a bluff.

82
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:55,610
I just want to use my own ability

83
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:58,000
to prove that I deserve
to be in this position.

84
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,860
How to prove it?

85
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,820
By pleasing everyone?

86
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,800
I admit,

87
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,360
I can't suddenly become someone

88
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,720
who ignores others' opinions

89
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,920
and lays down the law.

90
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,430
But that might not be the only way

91
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:10,000
to be a good forewoman.

92
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:13,720
I just want to find a way that suits me.

93
00:05:15,890 --> 00:05:17,570
Let me give you some advice.

94
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:19,240
Before you've fully

95
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,190
established your authority,

96
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,870
rumors like people saying

97
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,190
you got here through connections

98
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:25,830
aren't entirely bad.

99
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:29,040
It all depends on how you use them—

100
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:32,070
handled well, they can actually
work to your advantage.

101
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,159
What do you mean?

102
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,120
Keep it up.

103
00:05:46,870 --> 00:05:49,800
According to Article 47

104
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,700
of the Purong Hotel Quality Management
Rewards and Penalties Policy,

105
00:05:50,700 --> 00:05:56,490
[Purong Hotel]

106
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:52,070
if management is negligent,

107
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:53,270
dereliction of duty,

108
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:54,690
and command errors

109
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,130
that cause the hotel

110
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,770
serious financial and reputational losses,

111
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:01,160
they shall face
severe disciplinary action,

112
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,240
including demotion
or removal from their position.

113
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,120
Mr. Ji,

114
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:06,070
do you want me

115
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:08,270
to bear such a big responsibility alone?

116
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:11,430
I'm just a junior
HSKP Department manager.

117
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:14,160
I can't take on such a big responsibility.

118
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,950
This large-scale linen replacement alone

119
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:18,600
comes with a cost difference of over
a million just from the turnover.

120
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,540
On top of that, there are
the PR crisis media expenses,

121
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:22,630
the costs of the
complimentary stay promotions,

122
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:24,680
and the contract fees
for switching laundry vendors.

123
00:06:24,130 --> 00:06:26,090
[Purong Hotel]

124
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:27,360
HSKP Department

125
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,560
is tied to a huge portion
of the hotel's revenue and cash flow.

126
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,430
You know that.

127
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:32,800
I...

128
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,640
Mr. Ji,

129
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,630
don't scare Mr. Feng.

130
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,360
Anyone hearing this might think you're
about to audit him down to the last penny.

131
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,830
Besides, if the books
aren't settled by year-end,

132
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:44,730
you can't really tell
profit from loss anyway,

133
00:06:44,730 --> 00:06:45,530
right?

134
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,159
We know

135
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:49,430
you've just taken office,

136
00:06:49,430 --> 00:06:50,920
so you're sweeping clean.

137
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,000
We all understand.

138
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,159
But

139
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,920
we do hope you can also

140
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,630
appreciate how difficult things
are for those of us working under you.

141
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,870
Some things

142
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,830
may sound easy to say,

143
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,680
but they're not nearly
as simple to carry out.

144
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:06,680
It is inevitable to make mistakes at work.

145
00:07:06,710 --> 00:07:08,540
Please go easy on us, Mr. Ji.

146
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,430
Yeah.

147
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,950
If we strictly

148
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:12,190
follow the rules,

149
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:14,090
none of us will make any money.

150
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:14,750
You might as well

151
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:15,920
just fine us all.

152
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,000
Fine.

153
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:27,000
I respect everyone's opinion.

154
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:30,810
Then keep your position as Director Feng

155
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:33,260
but his quarterly bonus will be deducted.

156
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,750
He'll be given a major demerit

157
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:36,350
and a hotel-wide criticism.

158
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,850
Any objections?

159
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,190
I scheduled a shift for you,

160
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,520
and you're being picky?

161
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,360
Do I have to beg you to work?

162
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:55,240
Director, I really can't
work the night shift today.

163
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,600
If you can't work, then get out!

164
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,740
Get as far away as possible!

165
00:07:57,740 --> 00:07:58,630
I'm sorry.

166
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:08,830
What are you staring at?

167
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,160
Don't you know me?

168
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,850
If you're not eating, get out!

169
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,360
What kind of crappy food is this?

170
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,430
I'm not eating!

171
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:24,100
What are you looking at?

172
00:08:24,370 --> 00:08:25,460
Just eat!

173
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,150
Is that drunkard Feng crazy?

174
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,440
Why is he yelling at everyone?

175
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,440
Didn't you know?

176
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,840
Because of the bleach incident,

177
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,630
he was publicly criticized
by the whole hotel.

178
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:40,559
The penalty is still posted
on the official website.

179
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,750
Everyone knows he's
a parasite in the hotel.

180
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,810
Someone finally taught him a lesson.

181
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,800
Then I must order a milk tea
to celebrate today.

182
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,790
Count me in.

183
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:00,690
From today on,

184
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:03,720
please have all departments
follow the Purong Hotel service rules

185
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,500
to self-check for issues.

186
00:09:04,430 --> 00:09:07,280
[Purong Hotel]

187
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,150
Strengthen management,

188
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:07,670
upgrade basic employee training,

189
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:12,690
[Making guests feel at home]

190
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:09,800
and conduct regular assessments.

191
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:15,510
Three receptionists must be on duty
during off-peak hours.

192
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:17,360
Other on-duty staff
should make full use of their time

193
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:22,070
[Convenience Handbook]

194
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,200
to improve foreign language skills

195
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,960
and familiarize themselves
with information around the hotel.

196
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:24,090
On-duty staff must keep
hospitality etiquette in mind.

197
00:09:24,210 --> 00:09:26,670
Phones must be answered
within three rings.

198
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,500
Hello, Purong Hotel at your service.

199
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:31,470
Yes, we do.

200
00:09:34,830 --> 00:09:36,290
The logistics department

201
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:41,120
is responsible for restoring Purong's
tradition of displaying jasmine flowers.

202
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:54,240
All areas must ensure to always provide

203
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,190
the best all-around experience for guests,

204
00:09:56,190 --> 00:09:59,650
including visual, olfactory,
auditory, and tactile senses.

205
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,840
I hope everyone in the hotel
works together.

206
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,940
Let's bring back the original intention
of making guests feel at home

207
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:30,910
to Purong.

208
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,240
Jia, are you done with your work?

209
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:42,150
The guests in rooms 16, 17, and 18
have checked out.

210
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,320
Go and clean them up.

211
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,440
I have a headache.

212
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,120
I think I'm sick.

213
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:49,370
Find someone else.

214
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:56,390
Yin Xiang.

215
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,750
Stop right there, Miyu.

216
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,040
I still have a bunch of work to do.

217
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:02,000
You can't just exploit me

218
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,600
because we're on good terms.

219
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,320
Is anyone else free right now?

220
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,270
Jia,

221
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:30,150
if you're not feeling well,

222
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:31,320
go see a doctor.

223
00:11:31,510 --> 00:11:32,360
Bring back a doctor's note,

224
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,000
and I'll let you go home to rest.

225
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,910
Go now.

226
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,950
I got my period,

227
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,230
and my stomach hurts.

228
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:42,200
You got your period twice in half a month?

229
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,120
Are you okay?

230
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:46,440
Health is the most important thing.

231
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,510
If your body

232
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:49,510
can't handle the current workload,

233
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:50,550
that's okay.

234
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:51,630
Don't push yourself.

235
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,080
I'll help you talk to HR.

236
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:54,910
No need.

237
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,260
It's not that serious.

238
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:58,150
I feel much better now.

239
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,200
Glad to hear that.

240
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,500
If you can manage,

241
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,660
I'll still leave 16, 17, and 18 to you.

242
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:11,240
What's going on today?

243
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,170
Why isn't she buying this anymore?

244
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,660
What are you doing?

245
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:39,720
You startled me!

246
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,050
I wasn't doing anything.

247
00:12:42,050 --> 00:12:43,750
How could you just go through
a guest's things?

248
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:44,670
I was just looking.

249
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:45,790
I didn't take anything.

250
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,550
Besides,

251
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:48,360
this guest's belongings
are scattered everywhere.

252
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,840
How am I supposed to clean up
if I can't touch them?

253
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,200
Is this what you call cleaning up?

254
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,660
You cleaned them
right into the guest's bag.

255
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,360
Is this fine now?

256
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:01,910
Jia, let me tell you,

257
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,440
don't push your luck

258
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,140
to do these borderline things.

259
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,270
If something goes wrong,

260
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:09,130
you won't even be able to
explain yourself clearly.

261
00:13:13,930 --> 00:13:15,750
I haven't finished yet.

262
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,360
Are you done?

263
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:19,550
You've been targeting me since morning!

264
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:20,670
Don't bully me too much!

265
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:22,370
I should be the one saying that.

266
00:13:22,370 --> 00:13:23,560
Let me tell you, Jia.

267
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:25,870
It's fine if you have a problem with me.

268
00:13:25,870 --> 00:13:27,000
But as an attendant,

269
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,790
you lead the other attendants

270
00:13:28,790 --> 00:13:29,670
to slack off.

271
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:30,800
Isn't this too much?

272
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,030
Also,

273
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:32,990
please remember,

274
00:13:32,990 --> 00:13:33,910
I am your forewoman,

275
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:34,840
not your enemy.

276
00:13:34,980 --> 00:13:36,270
I just checked Room 1818,

277
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,390
which you are responsible for.

278
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:38,600
It's not cleaned up to standard.

279
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,150
After you finish cleaning this room,

280
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:41,480
go clean that one again.

281
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,330
Who are you trying to scare?

282
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,040
Aren't you just a forewoman?

283
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:47,670
So what if you're good at currying favor
with management?

284
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,530
Let me tell you,

285
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:50,880
if you want it cleaned, do it yourself.

286
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,360
Ms. Xu,

287
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,790
can you carry it alone?

288
00:14:09,140 --> 00:14:09,970
Yes, I can.

289
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:11,320
Hello.

290
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:12,390
Hello, sir.

291
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,440
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

292
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,990
[Passport]

293
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,640
I have a reservation.

294
00:14:15,540 --> 00:14:16,670
Excuse me, I was wondering

295
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:17,960
if Amber Santos' installation exhibition

296
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,000
is around here?

297
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:21,190
Please wait a moment, sir.

298
00:14:21,190 --> 00:14:22,400
[Convenience Handbook]

299
00:14:27,910 --> 00:14:29,150
I'm sorry, sir.

300
00:14:29,170 --> 00:14:30,300
I don't really know.

301
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,480
It's fine.

302
00:14:32,110 --> 00:14:33,510
Are you looking for Amber Santos's

303
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,650
Four Seasons Art Exhibition?

304
00:14:34,650 --> 00:14:35,640
Yes, that's the one.

305
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:37,440
This exhibition is indeed hard to find.

306
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,790
It's in the art space on the eighth floor

307
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:40,010
of the mall next door.

308
00:14:40,220 --> 00:14:41,440
There are posters up there.

309
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,600
You'll see them when you get up there.

310
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:43,870
Just follow the directions.

311
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:44,360
Okay, okay.

312
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,200
I've asked quite a few people,

313
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:45,720
and no one seems to know.

314
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,910
This exhibition just opened in Shanghai,

315
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,390
so it's normal that many people
don't know about it yet.

316
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:51,000
But it should close at 7:30.

317
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:51,750
Keep an eye on the time.

318
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:52,550
Don't miss it.

319
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:53,870
Okay, okay. Thank you.

320
00:14:53,870 --> 00:14:54,750
Glad to serve you.

321
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:55,680
Okay, thank you.

322
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:03,290
Sir, it's done.

323
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:05,260
-Thank you.
-Enjoy your stay.

324
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:10,720
Come in.

325
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:15,490
Mr. Ji, the finance department
is here to report the accounts.

326
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:16,330
Let them in.

327
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:17,190
Okay, come in.

328
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,080
Hello, Mr. Ji.

329
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,750
I am the accounting manager
of the finance department.

330
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:29,620
My name is Gao Fan.

331
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,910
We received a notice this morning

332
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,360
saying that you want to
check the accounts personally.

333
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:32,870
So,

334
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:34,320
we dug out these ledgers

335
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:36,550
for you from the warehouse.

336
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,750
However,

337
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:39,720
there's a lot of dust on them,

338
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,840
and the paper is quite brittle.

339
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,080
When you flip through them later,

340
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:43,410
please be very careful.

341
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:45,340
Where is your director?

342
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,840
You mean Director Huang?

343
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:50,160
He went out early this morning
with Mr. Wei to handle some business.

344
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:52,150
He handed these matters over to me.

345
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,120
Look here.

346
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:55,790
This cart

347
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:58,660
mainly contains details of supply amounts,

348
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:01,240
such as raw materials, consumables,

349
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:03,600
semi-finished products,
and warehouse goods.

350
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,150
You can

351
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:05,550
look through these freely.

352
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,300
This cart

353
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:07,790
is all about

354
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,480
operating expenses and production costs.

355
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:12,440
This cart is a bit messy.

356
00:16:12,630 --> 00:16:14,440
It mainly contains

357
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,790
detailed ledgers of fixed assets,

358
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:19,030
three-column subsidiary ledgers
for borrowing, lending, and balance,

359
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:20,910
and employee salary accounts.

360
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:21,770
That's enough.

361
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:26,460
Then I'll trouble you
to review them personally, Mr. Ji.

362
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:27,000
Okay.

363
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:36,550
Mr. Gao,

364
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,590
did you see Mr. Ji's face?

365
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,600
With all those carts of stuff,

366
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,960
if he doesn't get dizzy looking at them,

367
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:44,090
he'll at least get a dust mite allergy.

368
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:45,840
Didn't he want to investigate?

369
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,080
Let him.

370
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:50,520
Take his time to investigate it.

371
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,600
Why did you think of

372
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:57,840
treating me to barbecue today?

373
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,040
I just care about you.

374
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,510
How's the audit going?

375
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:02,960
As for the audit,

376
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:04,470
I originally thought

377
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:06,400
following the supply of linens

378
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,829
and cleaning fees

379
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:10,200
could reveal some discrepancies.

380
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,930
But the accounts are balanced,

381
00:17:12,349 --> 00:17:13,430
the receipts are complete,

382
00:17:13,430 --> 00:17:14,440
and there are no loopholes.

383
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:16,670
The finance department
is like a spider's web.

384
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:18,790
They won't let someone who just arrived

385
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:20,190
find any flaws so easily.

386
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:23,510
Rui,

387
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:27,310
stay and work with me.

388
00:17:27,310 --> 00:17:28,270
Help me.

389
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:38,300
You think I'm not sincere enough?

390
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:40,350
Come on.

391
00:17:46,990 --> 00:17:47,610
Ji Feng,

392
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,500
stop drinking.

393
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:49,970
Listen to me.

394
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,800
Actually, at this dinner today,

395
00:17:57,850 --> 00:17:59,180
I'm here to say goodbye.

396
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,440
I've already made arrangements

397
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:05,080
to go to Guilin
to be a financial director.

398
00:18:08,010 --> 00:18:08,720
By the way,

399
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:10,130
before I leave,

400
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,240
I have a gift for you.

401
00:18:12,510 --> 00:18:13,590
I hope it's useful.

402
00:18:23,130 --> 00:18:26,660
This is the account book I kept
when I was the head of accounting.

403
00:18:26,930 --> 00:18:28,020
[F&B Department]

404
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:28,710
[Handled by: Manager Chen]
[Handled by: Manager Jia]

405
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:31,780
The real accounts.

406
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:39,980
Later, they found out.

407
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:43,550
My career hit the ceiling.

408
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:45,760
Now I am the daily audit supervisor.

409
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,420
But honestly I'm just a nobody

410
00:18:48,450 --> 00:18:50,110
drifting around in the finance department.

411
00:18:50,110 --> 00:18:52,110
I can understand how you feel.

412
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:54,320
I've endured for so many years

413
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:56,720
and my skills are completely gone.

414
00:18:57,590 --> 00:18:59,320
I can't help you with anything.

415
00:18:59,650 --> 00:19:01,790
The little useful information I have left

416
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:03,190
has all been given to you.

417
00:19:08,570 --> 00:19:09,220
Rui,

418
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:10,880
here's to you.

419
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:13,390
May your career take off

420
00:19:13,410 --> 00:19:14,940
and everything go your way.

421
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,400
Ji Feng,

422
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,620
I'm ashamed

423
00:19:31,650 --> 00:19:34,110
I left you behind
to handle everything alone

424
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:35,840
while I ran off like a deserter.

425
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,920
I'll drink three glasses as a penalty.

426
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,440
Rui,

427
00:19:38,860 --> 00:19:40,050
you don't owe me anything.

428
00:19:40,050 --> 00:19:40,960
You have your future,

429
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,160
and I have my challenges.

430
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:43,890
We are going our separate ways.

431
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:44,930
It's just a pity.

432
00:19:44,930 --> 00:19:45,930
Why feel guilty?

433
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,480
No matter what,

434
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:48,890
seeing you find your place

435
00:19:48,890 --> 00:19:50,240
makes me happy.

436
00:19:50,330 --> 00:19:50,940
Really.

437
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:55,680
Cheers.

438
00:20:03,690 --> 00:20:05,530
Mr. Tan, time for your medicine.

439
00:20:07,650 --> 00:20:08,790
What do you always call me

440
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:09,830
"Mr. Tan"?

441
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:11,290
Call me Daniel from now on.

442
00:20:11,620 --> 00:20:13,450
You're making me sound old.

443
00:20:13,970 --> 00:20:15,540
Daniel, here you go.

444
00:20:16,670 --> 00:20:17,800
Just leave it there.

445
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:21,160
You still have to take it
if I leave it here.

446
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:23,530
You can't skip a single dose.

447
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:27,280
You don't want to
take your medicine again?

448
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:28,200
Fine.

449
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:30,180
I'll call Jizhou right now

450
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,730
and have him take you back.

451
00:20:31,750 --> 00:20:33,320
Eat, eat, eat.

452
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,200
Don't ever mention

453
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,770
Jizhou taking me back again.

454
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:39,750
Swallow it.

455
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:47,140
Do you often meet guests like this?

456
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:48,140
So disobedient.

457
00:20:48,270 --> 00:20:48,960
No.

458
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,300
Mr. Tan is very easy to get along with.

459
00:20:52,930 --> 00:20:56,290
Are you busy on the executive floor?

460
00:20:56,320 --> 00:20:58,940
Is the forewoman job going well?

461
00:20:59,530 --> 00:21:00,920
I'm working very well here.

462
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,920
Thank you.

463
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:03,240
You guys talk.

464
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,070
I'll get going.

465
00:21:04,070 --> 00:21:04,440
Okay.

466
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,030
Okay.

467
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:09,780
Good girl.

468
00:21:13,170 --> 00:21:14,130
We meet again.

469
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:15,050
It's you?

470
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,830
I'm looking for Daniel.

471
00:21:16,830 --> 00:21:18,270
I'm Tan Jiaming, his son.

472
00:21:19,220 --> 00:21:19,800
Come in.

473
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:21,590
Why are you here?

474
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:23,080
Auntie Wanjun is here too.

475
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:29,110
Ms. Xu.

476
00:21:31,620 --> 00:21:32,390
Thank you.

477
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:34,690
This exhibition is very nice.

478
00:21:35,260 --> 00:21:36,440
But what I'm more grateful for is

479
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,790
that you saved my father's life.

480
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:40,250
So this is a little token
of my appreciation.

481
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,680
I hope you can accept it.

482
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:44,130
[Amber Santos Four Seasons Art Exhibition]

483
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,090
I can't accept it.

484
00:21:44,090 --> 00:21:45,950
No, you must accept it.

485
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:47,400
I am really grateful to you.

486
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:49,440
I've never seen my father so happy.

487
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,700
It's all thanks to you.

488
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:52,860
Mr. Tan,

489
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,070
I appreciate your kindness,

490
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:56,070
But I really can't accept the gift.

491
00:21:56,070 --> 00:21:58,070
If you are really satisfied with
my service,

492
00:21:58,070 --> 00:22:01,070
then you are welcome to
visit Purong Hotel more often.

493
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,830
All right.

494
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,350
Ms. Xu,

495
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,620
you're really different.

496
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,160
Here's the thing.

497
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,440
When I chat with my father,

498
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,700
he often mentions you.

499
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,510
He said "Ms. Xu who takes care of me

500
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:15,200
studied hotel management,

501
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:17,270
but she has a great sense of art.

502
00:22:17,270 --> 00:22:19,130
It's a pleasure to talk with her."

503
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:20,850
Seeing you today,

504
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,160
I can see that's true.

505
00:22:24,270 --> 00:22:25,070
Thank you.

506
00:22:25,270 --> 00:22:27,110
Ms. Xu, can I ask you a question?

507
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:30,680
Why do you work as an attendant at Purong?

508
00:22:31,570 --> 00:22:32,300
I...

509
00:22:32,430 --> 00:22:34,630
I'm not trying to pry into your privacy.

510
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:35,790
It's like this.

511
00:22:35,790 --> 00:22:39,270
I think with your knowledge and ability,

512
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:41,920
you should go to a bigger platform

513
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:44,850
to do work that better reflects
your personal value.

514
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,350
So,

515
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:53,680
this is my name card.

516
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:55,270
If you need it,

517
00:22:55,130 --> 00:22:57,050
[Curator, Tan Jizhou]

518
00:22:55,270 --> 00:22:56,720
I can help you find work

519
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,270
related to the arts,

520
00:22:58,270 --> 00:23:00,310
and I'd be willing to
recommend you as well.

521
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,720
You are a curator?

522
00:23:02,030 --> 00:23:03,270
That's amazing.

523
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:04,830
Do you know me?

524
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:08,240
Then I guess I'm not amazing enough.

525
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,610
Well, Mr. Tan,

526
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:14,440
thank you for acknowledging me.

527
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,230
But I currently have no plans

528
00:23:16,230 --> 00:23:17,590
to leave Purong.

529
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,200
Because I think

530
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:21,400
being able to provide
every guest away from home

531
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:23,440
with a service that feels like home

532
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:25,330
is a very valuable thing.

533
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:28,310
So I really love my current job.

534
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:31,350
Okay.

535
00:23:31,790 --> 00:23:32,590
I understand.

536
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:33,680
If you need anything,

537
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:35,210
you can contact me anytime.

538
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:36,510
Thank you.

539
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:37,640
Mr. Tan, good night.

540
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,590
Good night.

541
00:23:52,070 --> 00:23:52,920
Mr. Ji.

542
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,030
You...

543
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:55,680
What's wrong with you?

544
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,200
Nothing.

545
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,600
I just had a little drink.

546
00:24:03,860 --> 00:24:04,900
Are you okay?

547
00:24:05,230 --> 00:24:05,990
I'm fine.

548
00:24:12,270 --> 00:24:13,200
I have the room card.

549
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:14,460
Let me swipe it for you.

550
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:19,370
Please come in.

551
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:48,750
Xu Miyu,

552
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:50,790
thank you

553
00:24:52,130 --> 00:24:52,960
for staying.

554
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,550
Sorry.

555
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:01,720
Sorry.

556
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:03,710
It's okay.

557
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:04,840
It's okay.

558
00:25:05,670 --> 00:25:06,530
I can handle it.

559
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:08,610
I can handle it.

560
00:25:09,150 --> 00:25:10,180
Thank you.

561
00:25:39,660 --> 00:25:42,930
[Zhao Ning – 19th Floor, Rest]
[He Xiao – 19th Floor, Night Shift]

562
00:25:39,830 --> 00:25:40,440
Ms. Xu.

563
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:41,640
Ms. Xu, are you there?

564
00:25:44,070 --> 00:25:44,510
Yes.

565
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:45,790
Come quickly.

566
00:25:45,790 --> 00:25:47,350
Jia has been held up by the guest

567
00:25:47,350 --> 00:25:48,110
in room 1817.

568
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:49,460
I'm coming.

569
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:53,200
Ke Wenxue,

570
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:55,440
do you have the information
of the guest in room 1817?

571
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:57,030
She's a middle-aged female guest.

572
00:25:57,030 --> 00:25:59,760
It seems she was upgraded
from the regular floor.

573
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:02,080
Okay, got it, thanks.

574
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:06,920
Hello, sorry to bother you.

575
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,920
I am the forewoman of the executive floor.

576
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,030
May I come in?

577
00:26:09,030 --> 00:26:09,680
Come in!

578
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:13,590
Hello.

579
00:26:13,810 --> 00:26:14,590
Sorry.

580
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:16,150
We have received your complaint.

581
00:26:16,150 --> 00:26:17,510
I'm here to understand the situation.

582
00:26:17,510 --> 00:26:18,310
Ask her.

583
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:20,270
I didn't take it.

584
00:26:20,270 --> 00:26:21,550
You're lying!

585
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,400
Hand over my diamond ring right now!

586
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:25,070
I didn't take her diamond ring.

587
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:26,460
I really didn't!

588
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,350
Excuse me.

589
00:26:28,510 --> 00:26:29,750
I am the general manager here.

590
00:26:29,750 --> 00:26:30,640
May I come in?

591
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:31,510
Come in.

592
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:50,920
This customer said

593
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,270
she lost a diamond ring in her room.

594
00:26:52,270 --> 00:26:53,550
She took it!

595
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:56,030
Look at how sneaky she is.

596
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:58,030
You were about to run
as soon as I walked in.

597
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:59,030
Why did you run?

598
00:26:59,030 --> 00:27:01,750
I had just finished cleaning the room
and was about to leave.

599
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:03,810
Have you finished cleaning the room?

600
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:05,720
Have you made the bed?

601
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:08,160
You even left your rag in the room.

602
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,270
If you didn't do anything wrong,

603
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:10,590
why were you panicking?

604
00:27:10,590 --> 00:27:11,920
When I entered the room,

605
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:13,270
I lost my diamond ring.

606
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:14,920
Please calm down first.

607
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,590
We will investigate this thoroughly,

608
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:17,440
and then...

609
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,030
Mr. Ji.

610
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:23,830
I have really checked this room.

611
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:28,300
Madam, I apologize

612
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:30,210
for your unpleasant experience.

613
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:32,480
May I ask how long
after the attendant left

614
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:33,680
did you call her back?

615
00:27:33,750 --> 00:27:34,790
As soon as I noticed something
wrong with her,

616
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:35,940
I checked my bag.

617
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:38,070
The diamond ring was indeed missing,

618
00:27:38,070 --> 00:27:39,510
so I went out to find her immediately.

619
00:27:39,510 --> 00:27:40,880
Hand it over right now.

620
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,590
I didn't take it.

621
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:45,030
Jia,

622
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:46,510
come in and check with me.

623
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:54,020
Excuse me, wait a moment.

624
00:27:58,440 --> 00:27:59,270
Alright.

625
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:01,310
Let me ask you,

626
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:04,110
did you take
the guest's belongings or not?

627
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,310
If you don't tell me the truth,

628
00:28:05,310 --> 00:28:06,640
I really can't help you.

629
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:15,720
I was just curious

630
00:28:16,340 --> 00:28:19,060
and searched the price online.

631
00:28:16,450 --> 00:28:17,340
[Moissanite Ring – 18K Gold Engagement
Diamond Ring, High-End Replica Ring]

632
00:28:17,370 --> 00:28:18,000
[True Love Lab-Grown Gemstone Ring]

633
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:18,910
[High-Quality 18K Gold
Six-Prong Lab Diamond Ring]

634
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:21,900
You rummaged through
the guest's bag again?

635
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:22,550
Okay.

636
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,440
Come with me and turn yourself in.

637
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:25,170
Sister Miyu,

638
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:25,720
I was wrong.

639
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:26,780
I really was wrong.

640
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:28,810
Please, listen to my explanation.

641
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,030
I thought

642
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:32,180
it was just a small matter.

643
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:15,860
[Search for Similar Items]

644
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:17,580
[Moissanite–
Birthday Gift for Girlfriend]

645
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:18,030
I wouldn't want it

646
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:18,540
[S990 sterling silver little snake ring]

647
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:19,280
[Minimalist sterling silver tail ring
for men and women]

648
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:20,510
even if she gave it to me.

649
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:23,720
I knew it was a fake.

650
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:26,570
But it was just such a coincidence.

651
00:29:28,350 --> 00:29:29,410
What are you doing?

652
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:30,310
Not making a sound,

653
00:29:30,310 --> 00:29:30,830
you scared me!

654
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,590
Sorry. Sorry.

655
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,680
I realized right then
that something was wrong.

656
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,000
Fortunately, I caught her.

657
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:41,510
I...

658
00:29:44,490 --> 00:29:45,920
Our staff will be right here.

659
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,550
Please wait a moment.

660
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:51,030
It's over.

661
00:29:51,960 --> 00:29:53,680
She's going to get sued.

662
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:54,650
She deserves it.

663
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:57,080
If she's got sticky fingers,
she shouldn't be working as an attendant.

664
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:58,590
Is this your first day knowing Jia?

665
00:29:58,590 --> 00:30:00,600
She only acts tough on the outside.

666
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:02,760
She doesn't have the guts to steal.

667
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:04,800
How long do I have to wait?

668
00:30:05,030 --> 00:30:06,160
Can you hurry up?

669
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:07,680
I don't know if our forewoman

670
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:08,980
can settle this.

671
00:30:09,270 --> 00:30:11,790
Jia and Ms. Xu fell out a long time ago.

672
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:14,950
I'm afraid no one can save her this time.

673
00:30:15,070 --> 00:30:18,060
It's hard to say if Ms. Xu
can even save herself.

674
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,510
Mr. Ji just took office,

675
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:21,440
and this scandal
happens on the executive floor.

676
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:23,500
This is a huge embarrassment for him.

677
00:30:25,030 --> 00:30:28,600
Even with Ms. Xu‘s strong backing,

678
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:30,070
she probably won't

679
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:31,600
escape the blame this time.

680
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:34,440
Stop looking.

681
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:35,070
Excuse me.

682
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:46,370
You can't just favor your own employees.

683
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:48,550
I told you she took it.

684
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:50,240
Why do you insist on searching the room?

685
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:50,920
Ma'am,

686
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,400
the situation is still unclear.

687
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:54,000
It might just be a misunderstanding.

688
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,730
What's wrong with this toilet?

689
00:30:57,550 --> 00:30:58,640
Dare.

690
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:00,720
This toilet has been clogged for ages.

691
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,380
The water won't go down at all.

692
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,160
What are you doing?

693
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,110
I asked you to find my stuff.

694
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:06,590
Why are you plunging the toilet?

695
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:07,160
Go.

696
00:31:17,750 --> 00:31:19,270
Mr. Ji, the security footage
you asked for is ready.

697
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:21,000
Mr. Ji, we didn't find the ring.

698
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:22,270
Okay.

699
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:24,200
Ma'am,

700
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:25,490
I need to go to the surveillance room.

701
00:31:25,490 --> 00:31:26,960
You can't just leave.

702
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,440
Are you trying to stall me?

703
00:31:28,550 --> 00:31:30,370
Get this straight.

704
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:32,790
I'm making things easier for you now.

705
00:31:33,570 --> 00:31:35,110
Problems that can be solved with money

706
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:36,160
aren't really problems,

707
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:36,590
right?

708
00:31:36,750 --> 00:31:38,920
I didn't want to
make a big deal out of this.

709
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:41,350
It's very bad for your hotel's image.

710
00:31:41,350 --> 00:31:43,810
But if you insist on
beating around the bush,

711
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:45,870
I'll have to call the police.

712
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,590
Two hours.

713
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:49,110
Give us another two hours.

714
00:31:49,110 --> 00:31:50,160
We will definitely find it.

715
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,110
I don't have two hours.

716
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:52,110
I'm checking out.

717
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,110
One hour.

718
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:55,790
Alright.

719
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,040
Just one hour.

720
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:02,200
[Notice of calling the fire police]

721
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:08,550
Mr. Ji.

722
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:11,770
Instead of looking for the ring,

723
00:32:11,770 --> 00:32:12,590
why are you following me?

724
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:13,790
That ring is fake.

725
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:15,480
Evidence.

726
00:32:15,770 --> 00:32:16,640
Jia...

727
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:21,030
I judged from the guest's attitude.

728
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:23,310
Normally, if someone loses
something so valuable,

729
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:25,640
they would want to know the truth

730
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:28,360
instead of just asking for compensation.

731
00:32:28,590 --> 00:32:29,350
However,

732
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:31,720
a 100,000 yuan ring disappears,

733
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:33,720
and she doesn't care how it got lost.

734
00:32:33,790 --> 00:32:36,000
She just opens her mouth
and asks for money.

735
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:37,270
I think it's very suspicious.

736
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:40,670
At a time like this,
you're still trying to shield your staff.

737
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:48,320
When you run into a guest
who frames you like this,

738
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:49,530
the only solution is…

739
00:32:49,560 --> 00:32:51,640
To find what she's hiding.

740
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,900
You have 50 minutes left.

741
00:32:55,900 --> 00:32:57,440
If you can't find the ring, you pay.

742
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:57,960
Me?

743
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,440
Why should I pay?

744
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:07,920
What are you doing?

745
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:08,830
I told you to look for something.

746
00:33:08,830 --> 00:33:10,690
Why are you digging in the toilet?

747
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,920
You all know how much

748
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,450
a one-carat diamond costs.

749
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:18,960
A random brand costs over 100,000.

750
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,640
I won't argue with you.

751
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,680
Let's round it off

752
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:23,120
and just pay me 100,000.

753
00:33:23,150 --> 00:33:25,400
Now you're the ones making trouble for me?

754
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,880
What terrible luck.

755
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:28,440
I'm going to the lobby to check out.

756
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:30,240
Call your general manager here!

757
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:31,590
Ma'am.

758
00:33:33,350 --> 00:33:34,110
What are you doing?

759
00:33:34,110 --> 00:33:35,000
I'm checking out.

760
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:35,720
Ma'am,

761
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:37,350
your ring hasn't been found yet, right?

762
00:33:37,350 --> 00:33:38,720
I brought a professional here

763
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:39,680
to help you look for it.

764
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,240
Please give us two more minutes.

765
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:41,960
You look for it.

766
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:42,790
I'm leaving.

767
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:44,160
This way, please.

768
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:44,880
Okay.

769
00:33:46,450 --> 00:33:47,560
What are you doing?

770
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:53,880
Miss.

771
00:33:54,710 --> 00:33:56,150
I can't take this toilet apart.

772
00:33:56,150 --> 00:33:57,720
They were all installed
by the manufacturer.

773
00:33:57,720 --> 00:34:00,070
If you want it removed,
the Engineering Department
has to follow the procedure.

774
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:02,270
I can fill out any paperwork
you need later.

775
00:34:02,270 --> 00:34:03,960
Can we just fix this emergency first?

776
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:05,000
No.

777
00:34:05,270 --> 00:34:07,470
Call me when you have all the paperwork.

778
00:34:07,750 --> 00:34:09,710
All talk and no action again.

779
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:10,440
Does your hotel

780
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:12,710
only play these childish games?

781
00:34:13,750 --> 00:34:14,400
Excuse me.

782
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:15,330
Coming through.

783
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,230
Rumors like people saying you got here

784
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:22,280
through connections
aren't entirely a bad thing.

785
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:26,090
If you handled well, they can actually
work to your advantage.

786
00:34:27,170 --> 00:34:27,909
Sir.

787
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:29,159
Wait a moment.

788
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:30,110
What is it?

789
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:32,090
Don't you know me?

790
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,360
I'm the new forewoman

791
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:35,150
promoted by Mr. Ji.

792
00:34:35,570 --> 00:34:37,739
If you want to follow the procedure,

793
00:34:37,770 --> 00:34:38,840
how about this?

794
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:40,239
I'll call him right now

795
00:34:40,270 --> 00:34:43,000
and have him personally
do the paperwork for you?

796
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,440
Okay, okay.

797
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:10,970
It's disassembled.

798
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:12,010
If you're done,

799
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,020
you call me.

800
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:26,670
Ms. Wang,

801
00:35:26,750 --> 00:35:29,030
-please wait outside.
-I'm just looking.

802
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:30,190
It smells bad here.

803
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:31,890
Sorry for the trouble.

804
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:53,870
I've found it.

805
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:00,400
This is a valuable item.

806
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:02,110
Our hotel needs to go through
an appraisal process.

807
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:03,000
Please wait a moment.

808
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:03,670
Appraisal?

809
00:36:06,230 --> 00:36:06,910
Mr. Zhu,

810
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,090
are you almost here?

811
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:09,320
There's no need for an appraisal.

812
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,150
Why go through all that trouble?

813
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,080
No need, no need.

814
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,590
Are you sure?

815
00:36:13,030 --> 00:36:15,920
This is a diamond ring worth over 100,000.

816
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:18,580
Our hotel absolutely
cannot take this lightly.

817
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,360
I'm sure.

818
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,770
What appraisal?

819
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:22,250
You are so much trouble.

820
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:25,000
Is there anything else
I can help you with?

821
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,920
We look forward to seeing you again
at Purong Hotel.

822
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:29,070
We are always at your service!

823
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:37,610
Mr. Ji,

824
00:36:37,850 --> 00:36:39,450
drink some more honey water,

825
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:42,110
and eat some apples
and oranges to sober up.

826
00:36:45,180 --> 00:36:46,100
Thank you.

827
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,030
About that jewelry appraisal...

828
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,400
There's no jewelry appraisal.

829
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,530
I was bluffing.

830
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:51,840
She knew her stuff was fake,

831
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:53,770
so she wouldn't dare to drag it out.

832
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:09,320
Miyu,

833
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,030
I'm sorry.

834
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:14,630
Thank you.

835
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:19,440
All right.

836
00:37:22,150 --> 00:37:23,540
Just learn your lesson

837
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:25,760
and don't do it again.

838
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:29,360
Go wash your face.

839
00:37:34,410 --> 00:37:36,670
As service staff on the executive floor,

840
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:37,590
our behavior

841
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:40,190
represents the service level
of Purong Hotel.

842
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:43,360
In this incident, Jia violated

843
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:45,710
Puyong Hotel's HSKP Department,

844
00:37:45,810 --> 00:37:47,070
Article 27,

845
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,710
by privately inspecting

846
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:50,110
a guest's personal belongings.

847
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:52,800
After a joint decision by
the HSKP Department and HR Department,

848
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:54,190
your monthly bonus will be deducted.

849
00:37:54,190 --> 00:37:55,250
Do you accept this?

850
00:37:56,290 --> 00:37:57,210
I accept.

851
00:38:00,310 --> 00:38:01,840
I hope this incident

852
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,320
will serve as a warning to everyone.

853
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,280
Don't think that

854
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:05,550
being late,

855
00:38:06,680 --> 00:38:08,080
gossiping about guests,

856
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:10,810
slacking off, faking an illness,

857
00:38:10,810 --> 00:38:12,730
slipping away, or skipping work

858
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:14,890
won't cause problems
just because no one sees you.

859
00:38:14,890 --> 00:38:16,610
I'm not doing this
to make things difficult for anyone,

860
00:38:16,610 --> 00:38:19,060
but to help everyone avoid risks together.

861
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:21,110
Workplace competition is certainly fierce,

862
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:22,170
but it's more about

863
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:24,060
cooperation and mutual benefit.

864
00:38:24,060 --> 00:38:26,390
I may not be your friend,

865
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:27,460
but

866
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:29,800
I am at least your partner.

867
00:38:33,990 --> 00:38:34,920
As the forewoman,

868
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:37,190
I hope whenever you have any difficulties,

869
00:38:37,190 --> 00:38:38,110
you can come to me.

870
00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:39,280
I will spare no effort

871
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:42,010
to help everyone
accomplish our tasks together.

872
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,560
There is only one goal.

873
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,800
I hope everyone can do their part

874
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:49,320
to improve the service
on the executive floor together.

875
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:50,190
All right?

876
00:38:50,190 --> 00:38:51,110
Yes.

877
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,990
[Wishing you prosperity and good fortune]

878
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:05,770
Miyu sent a really big red packet.

879
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:07,670
What does this mean?

880
00:39:07,890 --> 00:39:09,290
Penalties must be given,

881
00:39:09,370 --> 00:39:11,080
but compensations must also be made.

882
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,990
This is everyone's overtime pay
from last time.

883
00:39:12,990 --> 00:39:15,910
Although it's still less
than what you deserve.

884
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:18,420
I thought the overtime pay
wasn't approved.

885
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,540
Are you paying out of your own pocket?

886
00:39:21,210 --> 00:39:22,190
My bonus from last time

887
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:23,440
is completely gone.

888
00:39:23,700 --> 00:39:25,560
If you guys go against me again,

889
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:27,280
I'll have nothing to eat.

890
00:39:31,710 --> 00:39:34,070
Rooms 1805 and 1807 are checking out.

891
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:36,810
Copy that.

892
00:39:37,820 --> 00:39:38,610
Alright.

893
00:39:38,970 --> 00:39:39,970
Let's get to work.

894
00:39:51,940 --> 00:39:52,820
Xu Miyu,

895
00:39:53,040 --> 00:39:54,060
you can do this.

896
00:39:54,410 --> 00:39:55,880
You can be a good forewoman,

897
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:57,230
and do this job well.

898
00:39:57,470 --> 00:39:58,830
You can rely on yourself,

899
00:39:58,830 --> 00:40:00,830
and live every day of your life well.

900
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:10,340
[Purong Hotel]

901
00:40:13,630 --> 00:40:14,400
Mr. Qian.

902
00:40:15,150 --> 00:40:15,550
Mr. Ji.

903
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:16,210
Have a seat.

904
00:40:18,350 --> 00:40:19,010
Have a seat.

905
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:24,200
This is the reservation cancellation
form for Shijing Technology.

906
00:40:24,950 --> 00:40:26,080
Why was it canceled?

907
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,670
They were already quite hesitant.

908
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:29,280
Now,

909
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,550
with this whole bleach incident,

910
00:40:31,010 --> 00:40:31,810
[Cancellation of Reservation Agreement]

911
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:33,190
they are even more afraid to
give such a big order

912
00:40:32,020 --> 00:40:33,330
[Party A (Seal):
Shijing Technology Co., Ltd.]

913
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:34,190
to us.

914
00:40:33,470 --> 00:40:33,850
[Cancellation of Reservation Agreement]

915
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:36,400
Zhanpeng Industry is an old client,

916
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:38,630
