923
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:53,400
We also sent people over to visit,

924
00:40:53,590 --> 00:40:55,720
but they either said the boss wasn't in

925
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:57,710
or gave vague answers.

926
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:59,000
I figured,

927
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:01,280
since our agreement has expired,

928
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:02,880
this weekend I'll have

929
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:05,880
the front desk, housekeeping,
and finance settle the accounts

930
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,760
